title: Pitchfork's Top 50 Albums for 2008 (31-45)
description:
This is the third Torrent in a 4 torrent set - each torrent is in 15 album sets from Pitchfork's Top 50 Albums for 2008 - with an additional 10 albums (my favorites that were not included in Pitchfork's list) in the last set. Here is 31-45:

31. Fennesz - Black Sea 
32. Nick Cave And The Bad Seeds - Dig Lazarus Dig
33. Frightened Rabbit - The Midnight Organ Fight
34. Arther Russel - Love Is Overtaking Me
35. Girl Talk - Feed The Animals 
36. Wale - The Mixtape About Nothing
37. Grouper - Dragging a Dead Deer Up A Hill
38. The Bug - London Zoo
39. Times New Viking - Rip It Off 
40. The Very Best - Esau Mwamawaya Radioclit Are The Very Best
41. David Byrne & Brian Eno - Everything That Happens Will Happen Today
42. Bonnie "Prince" William - Lie Down In The Light
43. Shearwater - Rook 
44. Marnie Stern - This Is It And I Am It And You Are It And So Is That And He Is It And She Is It And It Is It And That Is That
45. Lykke Li - Youth Novels

As the list clearly demonstrates - it has been another amazing year in music - apart from the usual mainstream drivel that dominates the corporate airwaves.

I want to thank everyone in TPB community for making this one of the best torrent sites anywhere. May you all have a peaceful, prosperous and transfornational 2009. Enjoy!
